The paper discusses remote attestation (RA) for embedded and IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions time-sensitive and safety-critical applications, which suggests a systems (cs.SY) or software engineering (cs.SE) perspective. The use of low-end devices implies a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and networking (cs.NI).
